sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Dashboard User
    participant UI as Dashboard UI
    participant API as Dashboard Backend
    participant DB as Core/Mart SQLite DB
    participant MartSQL as mart_dashboard_views.sql

    API->>DB: Apply mart views (deployment step)
    DB-->>API: mart views ready

    User->>UI: Open platform quality panel
    UI->>API: Request latest quality KPIs
    API->>DB: Query vw_mart_dashboard_platform_quality_daily
    DB-->>API: Ranked KPI rows
    API-->>UI: JSON payload

    User->>UI: Select symbol (price deviation/curve)
    UI->>API: Request symbol analytics
    API->>DB: Query vw_mart_dashboard_price_deviation_daily
    API->>DB: Query vw_mart_dashboard_price_curve_24h_binance
    DB-->>API: Deviation + curve rows
    API-->>UI: Combined response
